# Complete Genome Assembly of the Antarctic Shag (Leucocarbo a. bransfieldensis)#

#Computational Workflow#
1.	Raw ONT read quality assessment
2.	ONT read filtering
3.	Illumina read quality assessment
4.	Hi-C read quality inspection
5.	De novo genome assembly using Hifiasm
6.	Primary assembly extraction
7.	Assembly quality assessment
8.	Hi-C read mapping
9.	Hi-C-based scaffolding evaluation
10.	Structural validation using Hi-C contact maps
11.	Manual inspection of assembly structure

